gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 118, Knicks 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Knicks, 118-100. Paolo Banchero recorded 36 points (6-10 3PM), seven rebounds, and five assists for the Magic, with Franz Wagner adding 21 points and six assists in the victory. Jalen Brunson tallied 33 points and six assists for the Knicks, with Precious Achiuwa adding a season-high 23 points along with 14 rebounds in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 30-25, while the Knicks fall to 33-22.
